## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited selection of articles and may not fully represent the entire spectrum of immigrant experiences in the U.S. Additionally, the perspectives gathered are subject to the biases of the authors and the publication platforms. Further research, including empirical studies and broader surveys, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the American Dream's status among immigrants.